ble than NNM and the\nproposed scheme outperforms many current state-of-the-art methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Feb 2017 04:28:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 May 2017 02:24:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 May 2017 01:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 31 May 2017 11:02:36 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 03:11:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-20"}
